---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Ayomiposi Sotomi"
  description="Writer. Builder. Security-minded human."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-text md:text-5xl">
      About
    </h1>

    <!-- DRAFT: personalize this in your own voice before publishing. -->
    <div class="prose prose-neutral mt-10 max-w-none">
      <p>
        I'm Ayomiposi Sotomi — a writer, builder, and security-minded human.
        This site is where those three things live together: essays on
        whatever's been sitting in my head, write-ups from homelab and
        Docker projects, and a running record of what I'm currently working
        on, learning, reading, and using.
      </p>
      <p>
        I used to scatter all of this across Substack, GitHub, and social
        platforms. This is the one place that's actually mine — no algorithm
        deciding who sees what, no ads, no cookie banners. Just Markdown
        files, committed to Git, rendered into pages that load fast and ask
        nothing of you.
      </p>
      <p>
        It's meant to be a quiet garden rather than a portfolio — somewhere
        that shows the process, not just the finished, polished output.
        Half-built homelab experiments get written up here too, not just the
        wins.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want to get in touch, find me on{' '}
        <a href="https://github.com/BlackJRoot" class="text-link hover:text-accent">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
